<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV98">
<l>tuñcā muṉivaru mallā tavarun tuṭaraniṉṟa</l>
<l>veñcāp piṟavi yiṭarkaṭi vāṉimai yōrtamakkun</l>
<l>taṉcārvi lāta taṉipperu mūrttitaṉ māyañcevvē</l>
<l>neñcā ṉiṉaippari tālveṇṇe yūṇeṉṉu mīṉaccollē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Straight away his magic is his solitary great form besides which there is no support</l>
<l>for celestials to chase away the affliction of birth without remainder,</l>
<l>in which stay consecutively the sleepless sages and others besides.</l>
<l>Difficult to think by the heart is the word of [his] degradation that calls butter [his] food.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
